    <div class="text-1xl py-0 font-bold"> Research Scientist </div>
    <br>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        My research focuses on the safety of artificial intelligence (AI)-based cyber-physical systems with an emphasis on the intersection of AI, systems safety engineering, and health technology. As a postdoctoral research scholar, I have developed a wide range of expertise in AI and safety-critical systems. In addition to my academic experience, I have gained experience in the automative industry developing automated driver-assist features (ADAS). My academic and industry experience has shaped my interest in advancing and expanding the boundaries of safety analysis and monitoring of AI-enabled technologies that impact human lives and the environment.
